<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="page-header about-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Story</h1>
    <p>Meet the three friends behind Trinity Woodenworks</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-content">
      <div class="story-block">
        <h2>The Beginning</h2>
        <p>Trinity Woodenworks was born in 2020 from a simple idea shared between three college friends — <strong>Anshuman</strong>, <strong>Sachin</strong>, and <strong>Sankalp</strong>. What began as weekend woodworking sessions in a cramped garage quickly evolved into something much bigger.</p>
        <p>United by their passion for craftsmanship and a shared dream of building something meaningful, the trio decided to turn their hobby into a business. They named it "Trinity" to represent their bond of three, and "Woodenworks" to honor their craft.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="founders-grid">
        <div class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></div>
          <h3>Anshuman</h3>
          <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder & Design Lead</p>
          <p>Anshuman brings creative vision to every piece. His eye for design and detail ensures that each product is not just functional, but a work of art that tells a story.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></div>
          <h3>Sachin</h3>
          <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder & Master Craftsman</p>
          <p>Sachin is the hands behind our finest pieces. With years of woodworking experience and a deep understanding of wood, he transforms raw timber into exquisite creations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></div>
          <h3>Sankalp</h3>
          <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder & Operations Head</p>
          <p>Sankalp ensures everything runs smoothly — from sourcing the finest wood to delivering orders on time. His attention to quality control is what sets us apart.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-block">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At Trinity Woodenworks, we believe that wood is more than just a material — it's a living, breathing element that brings warmth and character to any space. Our mission is to create handcrafted wooden products that combine traditional craftsmanship with modern design sensibilities.</p>
        <p>We are committed to sustainability, using only responsibly sourced wood and eco-friendly finishes. Every product we create is built to last, reducing waste and promoting a culture of quality over quantity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i></div>
          <h3>Sustainability</h3>
          <p>We source our wood from sustainable forests and use eco-friendly finishes, ensuring our craft respects the environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
          <h3>Quality</h3>
          <p>Every piece is meticulously crafted and inspected, ensuring the highest standards of quality and durability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
          <h3>Integrity</h3>
          <p>We believe in honest business practices, transparent pricing, and building lasting relationships with our customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
          <h3>Innovation</h3>
          <p>We constantly push creative boundaries while honoring traditional woodworking techniques.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-block">
        <h2>Our Workshop</h2>
        <p>Located in the heart of Jaipur, our workshop is where the magic happens. Equipped with both modern tools and traditional hand tools, our space is a blend of old and new — much like the products we create.</p>
        <p>We welcome visitors to our workshop by appointment. Come see our craftsmen at work and witness the transformation of raw wood into beautiful pieces of art.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
